0these%20days.%20You%20just%20look%20comfy%20in%20that%20chunky%20knit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20you%20here%2C%20by%20the%20way%3F%20Are%20you%20nostalgic%20for%20the%20time%20when%20children%20responded%20to%20a%20children's%20TV%20show%20about%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20wasn't%20as%20sympathetic%20as%20the%20BBC%20had%20hoped%3F%20Perhaps%20you're%20younger%20than%20that%2C%20and%20are%20simply%20nostalgic%20for%20the%20time%20when%20a%20grown%20adult%20(me%2C%20hello!)%20responded%20to%20that%20nostalgia%20by%20being%20even%20crueller%2C%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%0A%3Cp%3ECruelty!%20It's%20funny%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20Seeing%20someone%20else%20act%20out%20your%20most%20savage%20and%20repressed%20thoughts%20-%20it's%20really%20exciting.%20So%20exciting%2C%20that%20it%20makes%20you%20want%20to%20rail%20against%20political%20correctness.%20Why%20shouldn't%20you%20say%20what%20you%20want%3F%20Who%20are%20these%20idiots%20taking%20offence%2C%20because%20of%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20words%20coming%20out%20of%20your%20mouth%3F%20YOU%20know%20you're%20not%20evil.%20So%20you%20set%20up%20an%20anonymous%20message%20board%20where%20you%20can%20say%20what%20you%20damn%20well%20like%2C%20and%20hound%20people%20you%20disagree%20with%20out%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20because%20FUCK%20THEM%20for%20telling%20you%20you%20can't%20call%20people%20faggots.%20Faggots%20is%20a%20word%20thats%20constantly%20on%20the%20tip%20of%20your%20tongue.%20Not%20saying%20it%20would%20require%20you%20to%20actively%20CENSOR%20yourself.%20And%20that's%20what%20BITCHES%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EI%20get%20that%2C%20I%20really%20do.%20It's%20despicable%2C%20but%20it's%20human.%20It's%20why%20I%20listen%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.distortedview.com%2Fshow%2F%22%3EDistorted%20View%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%20Listen%20to%20that%20podcast%2C%20by%20the%20way.%20It's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20condense%20your%20evil%20into%20a%20disgusting%20half-hour%20of%20the%20day%2C%20before%20resuming%20treating%20the%20people%20around%20you%20with%20a%20subtle%20parody%20of%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20this%20page%20began%20when%20there%20was%20no%20other%20information%20on%20the%20web%20about%20Joey.%20When%20Yahoo%20was%20the%20Argos%20%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20we%20weren't%20shouting%20OK%20GOOGLE%20FUCKING%20NO%20WAIT%20OK%20GOOGLE%20at%20our%20wristwatches.%20The%20cruelty%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20the%20deliciously%20tangy%20sauce%2C%20slathered%20on%20a%20slim%20banana%20of%20information%20-%20having%20not%20experience%20the%20reaction%20to%20Joey%20the%20first%20time%20around%2C%20I%20was%20discovering%20the%20joy%20of%20responding%20inappropriately%20myself.%20Was%20it%20OK%3F%20No.%20Did%20it%20give%20a%20lot%20of%20otherwise%20decent%20people%20pleasure%3F%20Inexplicably%2C%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there's%20information%20everywhere.%20Joey%20has%20a%20Wikipedia%20page.%20My%20website%2C%20The%20Law%20of%20the%20Playground%2C%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20book%20and%20a%20TV%20show%2C%20in%20which%20actual%20celebrities%20pretended%20to%20remember%20him.%20%20My%20banana%20is%20redundant%2C%20and%20the%20sauce%20is%20sickly%20and%20nauseating%20without%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20bring%20myself%20to%20wish%20I'd%20never%20created%20this%20page%20-%20although%20I'm%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20I'd%20be%20a%20better%20person%20if%20I%20could.%20But%20this%20gleefully%20savage%20voice%2C%20punching%20down%20with%20such%20pleasure%2C%20is%20alien%20to%20me%20today.%20Maybe%20it'll%20become%20more%20alien%20to%20you.%20Maybe%20not.%20Perhaps%20you're%20a%20complete%20bastard%2C%20in%20which%20case%20I'd%20probably%20have%20casual%20sex%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EI'm%20slow%20to%20take%20this%20page%20down%2C%20because%20I%20want%20to%20hold%20my%20own%20repulsive%20feet%20into%20the%20fire%2C%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20come%20across%20like%20a%20preachy%20dick%20who's%20erasing%20his%20past%20to%20look%20more%20decent%20than%20he%20is.%20However%2C%20maybe%20you'd%20like%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.specialeffect.org.uk%2F%22%3Evisit%20the%20excellent%20charity%2C%20Special%20Effect.%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20help%20people%20with%20physical%20disability%20enjoy%20video%20games%20-%20something%20that's%20nowhere%20near%20as%20trivial%20as%20it%20sounds.%20It's%20genuinely%20life-improving%20stuff.%20So%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20the%20bad%20guy%20with%20me%20and%20laugh%20at%20this%2C%20at%20least%20balance%20it%20out%20with%20a%20donation%20to%20some%20good%20fuckers%20who%20spend%20their%20entire%20days%20doing%20the%20right%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EGood%20day%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EI%20SAID%20GOOD%20DAY%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
    },
